title: The Morning After I Became Just Like My Parents
itunes:title: The Morning After I Became Just Like My Parents
description: Kelly's on the road and hopping on the mic from her parent's house in Atlanta to update y'all on the last two weeks. She talks about Sean McVay's wedding, her friend trip to Tulum, traveling with all 4 girls & a special surprise announcement for everyone at the end!The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA. Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup @kbstafford89@themorningafter.kellystafford
